    ("Next.js: Server Components", "Default in App Router. Run on server. Can access DB directly.", "// Server Component (default)\nexport default async function Page() {\n    const data = await db.query(); // Direct DB!\n    return <List data={data} />;\n}\n\n// Client Component\n'use client'\nexport function Counter() {\n    const [count, setCount] = useState(0);\n    return <button onClick={() => setCount(c => c+1)}>{count}</button>;\n}", "Game: Where do Server Components run?\nA) Browser\nB) Server\nC) Both", "Where do Server Components run?", ["Browser", "Server", "Both", "Neither"], 1, "Server Components run on the server. Can access DB directly."),
